  "prompt": "What are best prostate cancer websites?",
  "response": "Here are some highly recommended websites for prostate cancer information:\n\n1. Medical Organizations\n- American Cancer Society (cancer.org)\n- National Cancer Institute (cancer.gov)\n- Prostate Cancer Foundation (pcf.org)\n- Zero - The End of Prostate Cancer (zerocancer.org)\n\n2. Support and Information\n- Prostate Cancer Research Institute (pcri.org)\n- Us TOO International (ustoo.org)\n- Prostate Cancer Support Association\n\n3. Research and Treatment\n- Memorial Sloan Kettering Cancer Center (mskcc.org)\n- Mayo Clinic (mayoclinic.org)\n- Johns Hopkins Prostate Cancer Center\n\n4. Patient Support\n- Prostate Cancer Support Group (prostatecancerinfo.info)\n- CancerConnect (cancerconnect.com)\n\n5. Clinical Trials\n- ClinicalTrials.gov\n- Cancer.gov/trials\n\nThese websites offer:\n- Latest research\n- Treatment options\n- Support resources\n- Clinical trial information\n- Patient stories\n- Expert medical advice\n\nAlways consult healthcare professionals for personalized medical guidance.",
